OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FAndy Burnham promised the biggest
OL,8,Fchange to British politics in 40 years
OL,9,Fas he became Prime Minister, making
OL,10,FJohn Healey his Chancellor and
OL,11,Fsweeping away key figures from Sir
OL,12,FKeir Starmer's government.
OL,14,FThe new Prime Minister promised to
OL,15,Fprovide early "breathing space" for
OL,16,Fhouseholds struggling with the cost of
OL,17,Fliving, vowed to end rough sleeping
OL,18,Fand set out a goal of
OL,19,F"reindustrialising Britain".
OL,26,@wD@OOUwD@_O]{D@AOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
