FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FSpeaking outside the door to No 10 Mr
OL,8,FBurnham said he would deliver "a new
OL,9,Fpolitical model and a new economic
OL,10,Fmodel" for Britain.
OL,12,FFormer defence secretary Mr Healey,
OL,13,Fwho quit Sir Keir's government in a
OL,14,Frow over funding for the military, was
OL,15,Fthe first new appointment announced by
OL,16,FMr Burnham.
OL,18,FEd Miliband, who had been widely
OL,19,Frumoured to be the next chancellor,
OL,20,Fwas appointed as Foreign Secretary.
OL,26,@pD@_OUrD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
