PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FShabana Mahmood, another senior figure
OL,8,Fwho had been speculated about as a
OL,9,Fpotential chancellor, remains as Home
OL,10,FSecretary.
OL,12,FLouise Haigh, a key ally of Mr Burnham
OL,13,Fwho was instrumental in getting him
OL,14,Finto No 10, has been made First
OL,15,FSecretary of State and Chancellor of
OL,16,Fthe Duchy of Lancaster, giving her a
OL,17,Frole as a fixer across government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
