PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FMr Healey replaced Rachel Reeves, who
OL,8,Fhe clashed with over cash for the
OL,9,Fdefence investment plan, as she left
OL,10,Fgovernment after turning down another
OL,11,Frole.
OL,13,FA series of other major figures from
OL,14,Fthe Starmer era were sacked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
