CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FSir Keir's deputy prime minister David
OL,8,FLammy, chief secretary Darren Jones,
OL,9,Fbusiness secretary Peter Kyle,
OL,10,Fattorney general Lord Hermer,
OL,11,Ftechnology secretary Liz Kendall,
OL,12,FWelsh secretary Jo Stevens, Northern
OL,13,FIreland secretary Hilary Benn,
OL,14,Fpaymaster general Nick Thomas-Symonds
OL,15,Fand development minister Baroness
OL,16,FChapman all lost their jobs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
