OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FStarmer loyalist Steve Reed, who lost
OL,8,Fhis Cabinet role at the housing
OL,9,Fministry, told Mr Burnham: "I hope
OL,10,Fthose who did not show loyalty to Keir
OL,11,Fwill now show it to you."
OL,13,FJonathan Reynolds' appointment as
OL,14,FBusiness Secretary with a beefed-up
OL,15,Fportfolio that included science and
OL,16,Finnovation, and Lisa Nandy remaining
OL,17,Fas Culture Secretary with new
OL,18,Fresponsibility for digital, meanwhile
OL,19,Fsuggested that the Department for
OL,20,FScience, Innovation and Technology
OL,21,F(DSIT) had been scrapped.
OL,26,@qD@\OUsD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
