PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FWes Streeting returned to Government
OL,8,Fas the new Defence Secretary in a late-
OL,9,Fnight appointment, while Miatta
OL,10,FFahnbulleh ` a member of Mr Burnham's
OL,11,Finner circle ` was made Energy
OL,12,FSecretary.
OL,14,FIn his first speech as Prime Minister,
OL,15,FMr Burnham ` whose return to
OL,16,FWestminster triggered Sir Keir's
OL,17,Fresignation ` acknowledged the
OL,18,Fturbulence in British politics which
OL,19,Fmeant he was the seventh prime
OL,20,Fminister since 2016.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
