PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FIt was, he said, a time for
OL,8,F"reflection and new resolution" and
OL,9,F"Britain needs to show the world that
OL,10,Fwe can regain our stability once
OL,11,Fagain".
OL,13,FHe acknowledged a disaffection among
OL,14,FBritons with politics in general.
OL,16,F"I know people at home are fed up with
OL,17,Fpolitics. I hear you and I want to be
OL,18,Fhonest with you ` we have not been
OL,19,Fgood enough, and we need to be better.
OL,20,FWe will be.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@_O]qD@AOUsD@FO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,F"We will make this moment a circuit
OL,8,Fbreaker for Britain, bringing forward
OL,9,Fthe biggest changes in the last 40
OL,10,Fyears ` a new political model and a
OL,11,Fnew economic model."
OL,13,FHe suggested that would mean putting
OL,14,F"life's essentials back under stronger
OL,15,Fpublic control to make them
OL,16,Faffordable" and using public spending
OL,17,Fto back British businesses.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@TO]vD@AOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
