PN,30710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FMr Burnham said he would set out a 10-
OL,8,Fyear plan later this year but promised
OL,9,Fmore immediate help to deal with
OL,10,Fsqueezed household finances.
OL,12,F"I can do something to give people
OL,13,Fsome breathing space now, some help
OL,14,Fwith the cost of living, and I will
OL,15,Fset out some of those measures
OL,16,Fstarting tomorrow, including how we
OL,17,Fpay for them," he said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FMr Burnham later told reporters he was
OL,8,Flooking at measures including rent
OL,9,Ffreezes, caps on bus fares and help
OL,10,Fwith energy bills although no final
OL,11,Fdecisions have been made.
OL,13,FThe new Prime Minister also promised
OL,14,Fto:
OL,16,F` Help more young people into work by
OL,17,Fchanging the education system and
OL,18,Fgiving them more support
OL,20,F` Build more council homes
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
