OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,F` Create a more "preventative state",
OL,8,Finvesting in people's success rather
OL,9,Fthan paying for failure.
OL,11,FHe said: "That is the fair and
OL,12,Fsustainable way to bring the welfare
OL,13,Fbill down, to meet our fiscal rules,
OL,14,Fand to honour our commitments on
OL,15,Fdefence to our international partners."
OL,26,@oD@QOUoD@dO]sD@JOUwD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
