PN,30713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FMr Burnham's ability to move is
OL,8,Fconstrained by his commitment to
OL,9,Ffollow the rules on spending and
OL,10,Fborrowing set out by Ms Reeves while
OL,11,Fshe was chancellor and his promise to
OL,12,Fstick to Labour's manifesto commitment
OL,13,Fnot to hike personal taxes for workers.
OL,15,FHe told reporters he would use "any
OL,16,Fflexibility" he could find within the
OL,17,Fexisting rules but "none of this is
OL,18,Fabout taking risks with the economy".
OL,26,@wD@`OUxD@LO]yD@TOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FThe decision to appoint Mr Healey,
OL,8,Frather than the potentially more
OL,9,Fradical Mr Miliband, as Chancellor is
OL,10,Fan indication of Mr Burnham's
OL,11,Fintention to calm the markets.
OL,13,FMr Burnham said his approach was about
OL,14,Fputting the "right values and the
OL,15,Fright standards" at the heart of
OL,16,Fgovernment.
OL,18,F"I will put the care of people at the
OL,19,Fheart of everything I do," he said,
OL,20,Furging Britons to "pull with me" to
OL,21,F"build a new national sense of unity".
OL,26,@vD@MOUwD@PO]zD@AOU{D@ZO]|D@SOU|D@`O]}D@
OL,26,AAOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
