CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FHis first call as Prime Minister was
OL,8,Fwith Donald Trump and Downing Street
OL,9,Fsaid he told the US president he hoped
OL,10,Fto show him "what Manchester had to
OL,11,Foffer during a visit in the future"
OL,12,Famid speculation next year's G20
OL,13,Fsummit could be held in the North West.
OL,15,FMr Burnham swept into Downing Street
OL,16,Fafter being asked to form a government
OL,17,Fby the King following Sir Keir's
OL,18,Fresignation.
OL,26,@rD@MOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
