CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784605665
OL,3,CNew PM Burnham promises sweeping
OL,4,Cchanges as he makes Healey his
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FIn his final speech as prime minister
OL,8,FSir Keir praised the "greatness of
OL,9,FBritain", and said: "I go with good
OL,10,Fgrace, I go with a smile, and I go
OL,11,Fproud of everything that we have
OL,12,Fachieved."
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@HO]qD@UOUtD@JO]
